# Rules

Rules are ways to enforce data security best practices across your codebase. Curio's summary report allows you to quickly identify rule violations in your code.

Curio's built-in rules aim to keep you protected from the [Top 10 Data Security Risks for Web Applcations]() and include a corresponding DSR ID to help you identify the risk.

